snippet.title: Hearts of Iron IV: Götterdämmerung | Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Hearts of Iron IV: Götterdämmerung - available NOW! https://pdxint.at/EP1Store

Brace for the Gathering Storm! Raid your enemies, build a powerful army and take over the world. Explore new alternate histories and geopolitical options for the key player in World War II: the German Reich, or take up arms as Austria, Hungary or Belgium and fight back.  

#hoi4 #heartsofironiv #götterdämmerung
